                     <interp inst="t18430403-1282-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18430403-1282-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp> for uttering counterfeit coin.</rs>
