                        <interp inst="t18430403-name-967" type="given" value="LUKE"></interp>LUKE NIXON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable B</hi> 16.) I took the prisoner, and received the half-crown from John Betts—the prisoner stated he got it from a coach-man, in Kennorton-street—I asked his own name and address—he refused to give it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
